                    <div class="l-article__body c-article__body" data-io-article-url="/1373019-us-election-trump-doubtful-2nd-debate-contracting-covid-19.html">
                <p class="align-left"><strong>- Donald Trump said he would not partake in the second presidential debate with Joe Biden</strong></p><div id="js-adfox-intext"></div><div id="js-adfox-scrollroll"></div><p class="align-left"><strong>- The matchup is scheduled to hold on Thursday, October 15, with just weeks to the presidential election </strong></p><p class="align-left"><strong>- Trump said it would be ridiculous to hold the second debate virtually because his challenger may &quot;cut me off whenever they want”</strong></p><p class="align-left"><strong>PAY ATTENTION:</strong> <a href="https://www.legit.ng/1371221-independence-day-legitng-n115000-n75000-n38000-grabs.html" target="_blank">Win a prize of N115,000, N75000 or N38000: participate in Big Naija Independence contest by Legit.ng</a></p><p class="align-left">Donald Trump, president of the United States, has rejected a virtual option for the second presidential debate with the former vice president and Democratic challenger, Joe Biden.</p><p class="align-left">It would be recalled that the president of the United States announced on Thursday, October 2, that he and his wife Melania tested positive for <a href="https://www.legit.ng/1318151-coronavirus-engaging-activities-avoid-boredom-following-stay-home-order.html">coronavirus</a>. </p><div
            id="div-gpt-ad-1489746201402-0"
            class="c-adv c-adv--with-bg c-adv--vertical-padding l-adv l-adv--full-width"
            data-slot="/76590364/legit_intext"
            ></div><p class="align-left">Trump revealed his health status on his verified Twitter page, saying he and Melania have begun their quarantine process. </p><div class="l-article__read-also c-article-read-also"><a href="https://www.legit.ng/1372961-my-covid-19-status-blessing-god-president-trump.html?utm_source=direct&amp;utm_medium=rads"><img class="c-article-read-also__image" data-src="https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/11b27b7f07e852a7.jpg?impolicy=cropped-image&amp;imwidth=256" sizes="256px" data-srcset="https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/11b27b7f07e852a7.jpg?impolicy=cropped-image&amp;imwidth=256, https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/11b27b7f07e852a7.jpg?impolicy=cropped-image&amp;imwidth=512"></a><a class="c-article-read-also__headline" href="https://www.legit.ng/1372961-my-covid-19-status-blessing-god-president-trump.html?utm_source=direct&amp;utm_medium=rads"><span class="c-article-read-also__headline-hover-inner">Why I'm happy I contracted COVID-19 - President Trump (video)</span></a></div><p class="align-left">The US president&#39;s Covid-19 status came on the heels of several conspiracy theories and counter-arguments on the existence and cure of the virus capped by open confrontation with China where the virus originated.</p><div class="article-image" style="width:900px"><img class="article-image__picture" width="900" alt="US election: Trump doubtful for 2nd presidential debate after contracting Covid-19" title="US election: Trump doubtful for 2nd presidential debate after contracting Covid-19" data-src="https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/c3242fd1bfc6ed2c.jpg?imwidth=900"><p class="article-image__caption">President Donald Trump said he would not partake in the second presidential debate with Joe Biden.
Credit: Reuters.<br>Source: UGC</p></div><p class="align-left">Meanwhile,<strong> Legit.ng</strong> had reported that it was a typically tensed atmosphere in Ohio as Trump and his Biden met face-to-face in their first presidential debate ahead of the United States election.</p><p class="align-left">Trump pulled the stunts on both his opponent and the moderator in a bid to hold the spotlight from the historical matchup while Biden also fired back in a debate grossly characterised by personal attacks and name-callings.</p><p class="align-left">The president has now rejected the second debate which is to hold virtually in order to stop the spread of the coronavirus infection.</p><p class="align-left"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election/trump-positive-for-covid-19-says-wont-participate-in-virtual-debate-idUSKBN26T1MP" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">According to Reuters</a>, the presidential debate is billed to hold on Thursday, October 15. </p><p class="align-left">Trump said it will be ridiculous to continue with the event virtually in what cast a spell of doubt on the possibility of the matchup taking place.</p><div class="l-article__read-also c-article-read-also"><a href="https://www.legit.ng/1372809-us-vp-debate-3-takeaways-matchup-harris-pence.html?utm_source=direct&amp;utm_medium=rads"><img class="c-article-read-also__image" data-src="https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/675f4d89011fdf3e.jpg?impolicy=cropped-image&amp;imwidth=256" sizes="256px" data-srcset="https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/675f4d89011fdf3e.jpg?impolicy=cropped-image&amp;imwidth=256, https://netstorage-legit.akamaized.net/images/675f4d89011fdf3e.jpg?impolicy=cropped-image&amp;imwidth=512"></a><a class="c-article-read-also__headline" href="https://www.legit.ng/1372809-us-vp-debate-3-takeaways-matchup-harris-pence.html?utm_source=direct&amp;utm_medium=rads"><span class="c-article-read-also__headline-hover-inner">3 crucial takeaways from peaceful U.S VP debate between Pence and Harris (photo, video)</span></a></div><p class="align-left">Trump said:</p><blockquote>“I’m not going to waste my time on a virtual debate. That’s not what debating is all about. You sit behind a computer and do a debate - it’s ridiculous, and then they cut you off whenever they want.”</blockquote><p class="align-left"><strong>PAY ATTENTION</strong>: <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.naij.android&amp;pid=solomonovlink" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Get the Latest Nigerian News Anywhere 24/7. Spend less on the Internet! </a></p><div
            id="div-gpt-ad-1489747094101-0"
            class="c-adv c-adv--with-bg c-adv--vertical-padding l-adv l-adv--full-width"
            data-slot="/76590364/legit_intext_02"
            ></div><p class="align-left">Meanwhile, presidential hopeful Biden has <a href="https://www.legit.ng/1371349-covid-19-joe-biden-wishes-president-trump-wife-quick-recovery.html" target="_blank">sent a goodwill message to President Trump and his wife</a> Melania upon contracting Covid-19 infection.</p><p class="align-left">In a tweet on Friday, October 2, Biden who is a former US vice president — having served as Barack Obama&#39;s deputy — said he and his wife Jill wished Trump and his partner a swift recovery.</p><p class="align-left"><strong>4 implications of Trump’s ban on Nigerians from the USA</strong> | <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwd8fNhb8OPLPSNELSys9pg" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Legit TV</a></p><div class="embed-container"><iframe class="embed-youtube" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7UP7aP3dDTU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p class="align-left"> </p>            </div>
        
